{"product_id":"nurme-damask-rose-delicate-cleansing-facial-foam-150ml","title":"NURME Damask Rose Delicate Cleansing Facial Foam 150ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eRose Face Cleansing Foam is an effective way to clean your face and remove makeup, even on those nights when you’re very tired. For radiant and youthful skin, regular cleansing is essential, especially during puberty when acne can easily develop.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNo need for cotton pads, making it eco-friendly.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRose extracts leave your skin soft and prevent dryness after washing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIt smells divine!\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse it both as a makeup remover and a refreshing facial cleanser.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePump 1-2 times onto your palm and massage the foam onto face. In case of contact with eyes, rinse immediately. Rinse off the foam with warm water and dry gently with a soft towel. Face tonic or a light cream can be used to complete the cleaning ritual.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eRosa Damascena (Damask Rose) Flower Water, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate**, Glycerin*, Babassu Oil Polyglyceryl-4 Esters, Sodium Benzoate**, Potassium Sorbate**, Citric Acid.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*From vegetable source\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e**Natural cosmetics approved ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e***Occurs naturally in essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915896590663,"sku":null,"price":12.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-damask-rose-delicate-cleansing-facial-foam-150ml-218878.png?v=1739897179","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/nurme-damask-rose-delicate-cleansing-facial-foam-150ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}